OPTIC SYSTEMS: Installing and repairing optical technology

Category: Electrical
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Installing and repairing optical technology: targeting scopes,
low-light and thermal optics, camera and sensor lenses. Common
knowledge for anyone who services weapon sights or vehicle sensor
suites for a living.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

